Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:05.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我早已言說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:09.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}一步步走向你的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:14.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}一滴滴落在地板的淚水
